1
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:44,240
This morning,

2
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,359
my sister and brother-in-law

3
00:00:46,479 --> 00:00:47,960
did go to the temple to burn incense.

4
00:00:52,799 --> 00:00:53,799
That explains it.

5
00:00:54,079 --> 00:00:55,679
They must have offended some spirit

6
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:56,960
while they were at the temple.

7
00:00:59,039 --> 00:01:00,439
My sister and brother-in-law went to the temple.

8
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,560
What does that have to do with her?

9
00:01:07,599 --> 00:01:09,159
The Mayor

10
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:12,040
and his wife, who do you think they are?

11
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:15,040
He's the reincarnated Star of Literature.

12
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:17,959
He carries the Righteous Aura.

13
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:22,319
Ordinary evil spirits can't get near him.

14
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,760
They can only pick on

15
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,120
his daughter.

16
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,000
Right.

17
00:01:26,719 --> 00:01:27,519
Just tell me,

18
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:28,879
do you have a way to cure her?

19
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,120
Two silver dollars.

20
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,120
Two?

21
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,159
How can two cure a sickness?

22
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,280
How about one?

23
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,120
Hurry up.

24
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:44,879
Fine then.

25
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,879
The two of us...

26
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:47,200
will go prepare in the back.

27
00:01:47,359 --> 00:01:48,599
Quickly get your young lady

28
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:50,000
seated on the chair.

29
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,840
Look at that awareness.

30
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,319
Come.

31
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:53,640
Dongsheng,

32
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,680
come help out.

33
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:55,480
Take it slow.

34
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:02,680
The sun sets in the west,

35
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:07,000
darkness falls.

36
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,719
Sun sets in the west, darkness falls.

37
00:02:11,759 --> 00:02:13,520
I close the gates and bolt them tight.

38
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:15,560
Magpies and crows return to the hills,

39
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,240
sparrows and moths dart to the eaves.

40
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:19,400
Nine of ten homes have locked their doors,

41
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,039
only one house remains open.

42
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:23,080
Crack the whip, beat the drum,

43
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,039
summon the gods!

44
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,120
What's going on?

45
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:30,280
The spirit has arrived.

46
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,919
You were a cat from the heavens,

47
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:35,000
who nudged Queen Mother of the West's waist.

48
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,400
Queen Mother of the West grew vexed,

49
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,199
set on taking your very life.

50
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,800
This cat fled for its life.

51
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,400
Queen Mother of the West waved her flag,

52
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:44,280
set on taking your very life.

53
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:47,439
Set on taking your very life.

54
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,319
Is this real or fake?

55
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:53,280
Definitely fake.

56
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:55,319
My Master once said,

57
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,719
Spirit Mediums don't cross Shanhai Pass.

58
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:58,680
These two are obviously frauds.

59
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:00,400
Wait,

60
00:03:00,879 --> 00:03:01,960
why didn't you say so earlier?

61
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:03,280
I'd never seen one before,

62
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,439
so I wanted to check it out.

63
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,639
Queen Mother of the West,

64
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,479
which deities have been summoned?

65
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,960
First, Tang Monk and Zhu Bajie,

66
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,599
second, Sha Wujing and Sun Wukong,

67
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:14,080
third, Erlang Shen made manifest,

68
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,759
fourth, Ma Chao and Huang Hansheng,

69
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,759
fifth, Crazy Ji the Buddha,

70
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,719
sixth, the willow spirit of the rivers,

71
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:21,520
seventh, Huang Santai of the flying dart,

72
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,159
eighth, Leng Yubing of the former dynasty,

73
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:25,000
ninth, Hua Tuo to heal the sick,

74
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,479
tenth, Heavenly King Li from above,

75
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:29,800
Jinmu Nezha, the Third Prince,

76
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:33,159
leading a hundred thousand celestial troops.

77
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:37,439
Looks like the young lady's trouble

78
00:03:37,479 --> 00:03:38,560
is worse than Sun Wukong's.

79
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,000
Stop messing around.

80
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:41,159
I'm worried sick.

81
00:03:41,159 --> 00:03:42,360
Did you all hear that clearly?

82
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:44,120
Our spirit lady just said,

83
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,039
your young lady, in her past life,

84
00:03:46,039 --> 00:03:47,919
offended Queen Mother of the West.

85
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:48,960
Now in this life,

86
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,960
she's come to take her.

87
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:52,680
What can we do then?

88
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,400
Don't worry, don't worry.

89
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,479
Drink my holy water,

90
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:59,360
and the young lady will be cured at once,

91
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,800
turning misfortune into blessing.

92
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:02,759
See?

93
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:03,960
Now they're asking for money.

94
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,680
Who said that?

95
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,680
We never ask for money.

96
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:09,520
That's wonderful then.

97
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:11,199
We want gold bars.

98
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,039
What?

99
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:14,400
Where would I get gold bars?

100
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:15,719
How about this,

101
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:17,639
you cure the young lady first,

102
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,199
and when my sister and her husband return,

103
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,759
I'll pay you the gold bars.

104
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:22,600
Spirit Lady,

105
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,000
will that work?

106
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:41,680
Here.

107
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,920
Holy water bestowed by the Fairy Maiden.

108
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,519
Come, drink it.

109
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:45,720
You...

110
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:47,199
This mouthful of rinse water

111
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,680
is worth a gold bar?

112
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,959
This is no ordinary rinse water.

113
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,800
Back then, Zhang Guolao drank

114
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,680
half a sip our Fairy Maiden left behind,

115
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,000
and that's how he became an immortal.

116
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:57,920
Come.

117
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,519
Pry open this young lady's

118
00:04:59,519 --> 00:04:59,920
mouth for me.

119
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,279
Come.

120
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:01,000
Second Spirit...

121
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:02,000
I'll handle it.

122
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,639
Let me do it.

123
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:13,680
Qiuying!

124
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,040
You're awake.

125
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,399
She's awake, she's awake!

126
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:20,319
You all saw it.

127
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:21,759
This mouthful of rinse water,

128
00:05:21,759 --> 00:05:22,560
we didn't drink a drop.

129
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,120
The gold bar is out of the question.

130
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,360
But she still smelled

131
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,759
the scent of my holy water!

132
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:29,879
That's gotta be worth at least two silver dollars!

133
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:30,800
It's worth...

134
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,600
Two bucks, fine.

135
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,160
Here you go.

136
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,279
Good.

137
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:46,279
What are you looking at?

138
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,079
Let me tell you something.

139
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,639
It's not that Uncle's stingy.

140
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,920
Treating your illness today

141
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,240
cost me fifty silver dollars.

142
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:53,639
When your parents get back,

143
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,639
you'd better get this money back for me!

144
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,480
If not for me, you'd be dead!

145
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:58,199
Thank you, Uncle.

146
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:00,879
You like her.

147
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:06,959
Is it that obvious?

148
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,399
It's practically written on your face.

149
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,279
After being reborn,

150
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,399
a rich young lady

151
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,319
falls in love with a foot soldier like me.

152
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:16,720
Are you mocking me?

153
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:20,439
Thank you.

154
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:21,480
Let's go.

155
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,279
I'll buy you a drink.

156
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:22,720
Sure.

157
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:31,680
How did you know

158
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,800
to press something hard against

159
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,000
Qiuying's Feishu (BL13) on her back

160
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:34,680
to wake her up?

161
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:36,600
I read it in my Master's

162
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,480
medical book.

163
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:39,040
You know medicine too?

164
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,519
I definitely

165
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:42,720
don't.

166
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,560
How could I possibly know medicine?

167
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:46,759
My Master said

168
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:47,959
I've been a slacker since childhood.

169
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,759
It's just that one time...

170
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:01,480
What are you doing?

171
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,040
Shut up.

172
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,120
Talk about a lucky break.

173
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:16,920
By pure coincidence,

174
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,360
this medical book

175
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:20,120
described Qiuying's exact symptoms

176
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,279
and the treatment.

177
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:21,879
Dongsheng,

178
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:23,879
you always mention your Master.

179
00:07:24,319 --> 00:07:25,079
Who is your Master?

180
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,759
He is...

181
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,120
Old Drunkard.

182
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,160
Old Drunkard?

183
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:31,120
What?

184
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:32,279
You know him?

185
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,560
No, I don't.

186
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:35,920
Then why react so strongly?

187
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,560
The mood was just right, you know?

188
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,560
But I heard the Brigade Commander say

189
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,959
their unit once had a man

190
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,120
who could summon wind and rain,

191
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,519
and turn beans into soldiers—a true master.

192
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,360
He was called Old Drunkard.

193
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:46,480
That's right.

194
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,279
He is my Master.

195
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:50,720
But my Master doesn't

196
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,639
turn beans into soldiers.

197
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,519
He summons the Five Fierce Spirit Soldiers.

198
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:56,240
What are the Five Fierce Spirit Soldiers?

199
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,079
Speaking of the Five Fierce Spirit Soldiers,

200
00:07:58,319 --> 00:07:59,120
they're truly formidable.

201
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:00,800
Legend has it

202
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,079
that long ago, Emperor Xuanyuan's

203
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,399
fallen warriors,

204
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,199
by the Nine Heavens Goddess's power,

205
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,319
had their souls

206
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:09,360
sealed on Mount Tiezhao in Fengdu.

207
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,319
They were granted eternal life,

208
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:12,720
but in exchange,

209
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,680
they lost their free will,

210
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,199
forced to obey the commands of talismans.

211
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,000
So...

212
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:17,879
can you do it?

213
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,920
Of course.

214
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:23,000
Then let us

215
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:23,879
see it for ourselves!

216
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,360
All of you, get to sleep!

217
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:34,840
Dongzi!

218
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,480
Dongsheng!

219
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,240
What is it?

220
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,120
Dongzi,

221
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,320
there were ghosts last night!

222
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,080
Ghosts?

223
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,320
Ghosts!

224
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:44,399
Ghosts!

225
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:45,399
Come on, come on!

226
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:45,840
Let's go!

227
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:46,120
Take a look!

228
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:46,440
Look!

229
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:46,759
Come see!

230
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:47,240
Hurry, go check!

231
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:49,879
There's a ghost!

232
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:51,279
A ghost!

233
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,360
A ghost!

234
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,080
The ghost is cooking!

235
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:56,960
Alright, enough.

236
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:57,519
Stop crying.

237
00:08:58,639 --> 00:08:59,720
Act like soldiers!

238
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:01,159
Tell me what happened.

239
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,559
Last night,

240
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,360
he and I were on guard duty.

241
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:08,000
The two of us again?

242
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,399
Every single night, it's us.

243
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:11,919
What a hard life.

244
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:15,799
What's that sound?

245
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,480
Sounds like it's coming from the kitchen.

246
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:21,519
Come on,

247
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:22,279
let's go check.

248
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,240
Why is someone in the kitchen?

249
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:30,480
Who's there?

250
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,000
Who?

251
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:32,559
Speak up!

252
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:34,720
Who?!

253
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,600
A ghost!

254
00:09:53,519 --> 00:09:54,799
Burning water!

255
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,240
The cleaver was chopping by itself!

256
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:58,200
Yes!

257
00:09:58,519 --> 00:09:58,799
Yes!

258
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,320
That's truly bizarre.

259
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:04,559
You,

260
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,679
come inside with me and check.

261
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:06,639
Me?

262
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:07,159
Me?

263
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:09,720
Come here!

264
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:16,759
There's a ghost!

265
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:17,720
A ghost!

266
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,840
You said

267
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,039
this water was burning?

268
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:26,159
Yes.

269
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:26,799
Yes.

270
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,559
See for yourself.

271
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,679
Was it this knife?
